dc_title_s: 1930 Real Estate Plat-Book of the City of Trenton and Borough of Princeton, Mercer County, New Jersey (Title Page)
dc_description_s: The title page of the 1930 Real Estate Plat-Book of the City of Trenton and Borough of Princeton, Mercer County, New Jersey contains information about the publisher and the geographic scope of the maps contained within the book.|In addition to the title page, there are 58 pages including several indices - a Trenton map index delineating the sections depicted on each plate, a street index, an index to the Trenton City Atlas Page (CAP) numbers, a zoning map, and an index to the 6 Princeton Borough plates.
